/*
:name: mod_runtime_divisor
:type: error
:tolg: 1
:error: runtime divisor
*/
// `a % b` with a RUNTIME divisor has no hardware lowering — only a comptime
// power-of-two divisor, `% 3`, or a divisor provably larger than `a` lowers to
// shift/mask (tolg lower_mod).
comb foo(a:u8, b:u8) -> (r) {
  r = a % b
}
